reviewText:
One of the best surf videos out there, period.

TAylor Steele's videos always are my favorites, very good video as always.

Lots of locations around the world, the best surf on the planet, gotta love the music. THANKS TAYLOR AND SURFERS KEEP ROLLING.

We met Taylor in 2007 when they were working at the WCT with the guys here in Iquique, Chile. couldn't be happier awesome xperience ever.

I bought 2 copys of Trilogy. :)  cesarlillo@hotmail.com
